{"tid":454390,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲尼亞里: 不了, 謝謝","createTime":"2017-11-01T05:39:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T12:50:31.000Z","uid":131176,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4c5ad65e8d8f7012e17e71c4bc50ac88905f489c","tid":454390,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:39:15.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=xuRX9uJAygzHR0L88SaOry7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=746e582e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】李斯特城早前辭退了領隊沙士比亞，原來在委任佩奧前，曾希望雲尼亞里回巢救亡，只是被這名冠軍功臣回絕。<br />\n<br />\n雲尼亞里（Claudio Ranieri）於2015/16球季帶領李斯特城童話式捧走英超冠軍，可是翌季因為成績低迷已被炒。繼任人沙士比亞早前亦被辭退，意大利傳媒Corriere dello Sport就爆料，指李城找過雲帥回歸，但後者面對無情的李城，只簡單地回覆：「不了，謝謝。」 雖然Corriere dello Sport未有表示有關消息是從那裡得知，但現時執教法甲南特的雲尼亞里，最近的確曾接受他們的專訪，只是出街的內容，沒有任何一項是關於李城。 雲尼亞里在訪問中提及其前球會車路士今季的表現，指車仔戰績平平的主因是換了前鋒，由迪亞高哥斯達換上了艾華路莫拉達：「這個轉變不容易，DC是一名領袖，可以肩負起球隊，用憤怒去踢球，而莫拉達就只是一名運球者。當你換前鋒，就整套踢法都要換。」"},{"pid":"ff0132b884b3e318622785b672397e521769dd14","tid":454390,"uid":40422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"comdom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021c63f82d53a1800d1aaff20661f6500d3197ff","tid":454390,"uid":40422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c3247af0510d26e457b8e3bf6d7d14fa2f70f683","tid":454390,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢做得好, 係好多港男的示範"},{"pid":"9829b288270f59c1adebf97e8b208ef6b35f8109","tid":454390,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:43:35.000Z"