te>唔係佢教波問題 係成隊波心態出現問題 以為冇佢就拎冠軍 老實講 佢地成隊波 什麼也不是<br />\n睇kante佢被炒果日幾有心搵佢 其他果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃鳩圾</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 此POST主要讚佢回絕回頭草之功力</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 骨氣"},{"pid":"7ac6a96cf4602d2c8c809849172e114775125065","tid":454390,"uid":38938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:15:32.000Z","msg":"李城=港女"},{"pid":"60fd0b253bd5e66711a1609e9fbb7d0b079615c4","tid":454390,"uid":67225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"當你換前鋒，就整套踢法都要換。<br />\n<br />\ntorres <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224592ab6682cd1d95994a0250dd85eb6b58d8ea","tid":454390,"uid":25771,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"唔信李城有搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34655b37582394bd134cd22284a933aa9de705a1","tid":454390,"uid":38688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:21:33.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4a18224f17ae4dcfa02276a36e9dfe2c55ad9a","tid":454390,"uid":47007,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係佢教波問題 係成隊波心態出現問題 以為冇佢就拎冠軍 老實講 佢地成隊波 什麼也不是<br />\n睇kante佢被炒果日幾有心搵佢 其他果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃鳩圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢教波其實都有好多問題<br />\n無錯,佢執教任何一支球隊第1季係有唔錯成績<br />\n但到第2季就已經被其他對手睇穿哂戰術<br />\n而又無法轉用另一套戰術,結果下下第2季都俾人炒<br />\n羅馬果陣已經係咁<br />\n國米直情連一季都捱唔到<br />\n<br />\n仲有華倫西亞果期同埋羅馬果期<br />\n佢都有同球員發生不和,托迪話佢戰術保守<br />\n睇番佢既戰術,442係佢最鍾意用既戰術<br />\n雖然一開始對手唔適應佢個戰術而可以長勝好多場<br />\n但一旦被對手睇穿哂,佢又可以N咁多場不勝<br />\n華倫,羅馬,國米,李城都試過"},{"pid":"f53be7f1735140a1f1bd10685c2ec8ca74fed329","tid":454390,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"比我都唔返啦，當人狗呀"},{"pid":"3ea9e518aa7e31606f33de45afe381d9243dc4dd","tid":454390,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係佢教波問題 係成隊波心態出現問題 以為冇佢就拎冠軍 老實講 佢地成隊波 什麼也不是<br />\n睇kante佢被炒果日幾有心搵佢 其他果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃鳩圾</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 此POST主要讚佢回絕回頭草之功力</blockquote><br />\n有幾多領隊不和會返前顧主度做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上唔會啦"}]}